com.safenetinc.luna
Class LunaAPI

java.lang.Object
  com.safenetinc.luna.LunaAPI

public class LunaAPI
extends Object

This class defines the JNI interface to the LunaAPI native library that is used to connect the JVM to the cryptoki library.

In general these methods are intended only for use only by SafeNet defined classes. These methods may change at any time and you are encouraged to make use of other interfaces

CheckSessionState

public int CheckSessionState(int sessionHandle)
                      throws LunaException
Returns the PKCS11 state of the session. This is defined as:
  • 0 - read-only public session (full access to public session objects, read only access to public token objects)
  • 1 - read-only user session (full access to all session objects, read-only access to all token objects)
  • 2 - read/write public session (full access to all public objects)
  • 3 - read/write user session (full access to all objects)
  • 4 - read/write SO session (full access to all public objects, access to SO functionality

Parameters:
sessionHandle - A session handle

The PKCS11 state of the session
